The state and Nyeri government should build a museum in Nyeri town to commemorate Mau Mau fi ghters and the struggle for Independence, Senator Mutahi Kagwe (pictured) has said.The names of all those who struggled for Independence should be inscribed in the museum as a sign of honour, he added.Kagwe spoke on Monday during Jamhuri Day celebrations at Dedan Kimathi Kamukunji Stadium in Nyeri town.